---
title: Easy Baked Mumbai Yoghurt Chicken with Roasted Veggies, Creamy Slaw & Cashews
description: This gorgeous plate of colour doesn't just look good - it's a nutritionally balanced combo of succulent yoghurt chicken,
rainbow-roasted veggies and creamy, crunchy spinach slaw. Flavour is just written all over it!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
